Why ship moving? Question There's a hole in it!

1370
01:51:37.070 --> 01:51:43.866
Hull breach. port side fuel compartments 11 and 12.

1371
01:51:43.890 --> 01:51:46.530
What happening? Question.

1372
01:51:46.970 --> 01:51:50.750
The fuel is migrating to Adrian!

1373
01:51:55.330 --> 01:51:57.010
Eject bad fuel bay. question?

1374
01:51:58.190 --> 01:51:59.190
Yeah.

1375
01:51:59.430 --> 01:52:02.870
Jettison port fuel tank compartment 12. Confirm.

1376
01:52:24.490 --> 01:52:29.310
Jettison port fuel tank compartment 11. Confirm.

1377
01:52:29.750 --> 01:52:32.170
Eject other fuel bay!

1378
01:55:46.530 --> 01:55:50.150
One nanogram of astrophage
isn't enough to blow up a building.

1379
01:55:50.710 --> 01:55:53.770
The photon master gave him one milligram by mistake.

1380
01:55:54.210 --> 01:55:57.010
That's a million times the heat
energy that they're prepared for.

1381
01:55:57.290 --> 01:56:00.910
A measuring mistake killed my entire science team.

1382
01:56:01.010 --> 01:56:02.370
Doesn't matter. we have to launch.

1383
01:56:09.750 --> 01:56:12.690
If we miss the orbital window. it'll set us back months.

1384
01:56:12.810 --> 01:56:15.670
Yeah. but if no one's trained to
do the mission. it won't matter.

1385
01:56:16.010 --> 01:56:18.326
