1386
01:56:18.350 --> 01:56:21.010
We launch on schedule with a replacement science officer.

1387
01:56:21.450 --> 01:56:28.190
Okay. but... who? I mean that.

1388
01:56:45.450 --> 01:56:46.806
I'm not an astronaut.

1389
01:56:46.830 --> 01:56:50.730
I don't need an astronaut. I need an
expert on astrophage who's mission ready.

1390
01:56:51.130 --> 01:56:55.610
I'm not ready. I don't have any training.

1391
01:56:56.430 --> 01:56:57.430
Well. pick it up.

1392
01:56:57.850 --> 01:57:01.630
I'm not an astronaut. I put the not in astronaut.

1393
01:57:01.870 --> 01:57:05.350
I've never done anything. I've never
done a spacewalk. I can't even moonwalk.

1394
01:57:05.570 --> 01:57:07.310
I haven't done the whole pool thing.

1395
01:57:07.490 --> 01:57:10.530
No. no. no. this is just for the picture. For social media.

1396
01:57:10.610 --> 01:57:15.106
