This might be very hard for you to understand.

1401
01:57:26.770 --> 01:57:28.530
but some people are failures.

1402
01:57:28.730 --> 01:57:30.570
Some people don't rise to the challenge.

1403
01:57:30.690 --> 01:57:32.926
You've been present for every major scientific

1404
