1407
01:57:39.750 --> 01:57:42.090
Grace. you'd be in very cool company.

1408
01:57:42.310 --> 01:57:44.030
If you don't go. you die anyway.

1409
01:57:44.170 --> 01:57:47.326
Yeah. but I die in 30 years with...

1410
01:57:47.350 --> 01:57:48.350
With the rest of us.

1411
01:57:49.630 --> 01:57:51.430
