1419
01:58:58.930 --> 01:59:00.390
Movement detected.

1420
01:59:02.510 --> 01:59:03.790
Good morning. Doctor Grace.

1421
02:00:21.710 --> 02:00:25.690
I'll watch you sleep. uh.

1422
02:00:32.050 --> 02:00:36.630
