1427
02:03:34.370 --> 02:03:35.610
We have our predator.

1428
02:03:36.490 --> 02:03:40.083
Right now I'm calling it Taumoeba. And I'm sure

1429
02:03:40.107 --> 02:03:43.926
that when you wake up. you'll have a lot to say

1430
02:03:43.950 --> 02:03:48.330
about why that's a bad name. because
it's just an amoeba from Tau Ceti

1431
02:03:48.540 --> 02:03:51.366
and putting tau in front of amoeba. But I would

1432
02:03:51.390 --> 02:03:54.300
argue there's an elegance to that. a simplicity.

1433
02:03:54.580 --> 02:03:59.076
Let's not fight about it now. Let's just. we'll table it.

1434
02:03:59.100 --> 02:04:01.826
I did a test at different atmospheric variables

1435
02:04:01.850 --> 02:04:04.600
and fun fact. every time I introduced nitrogen.

1436
02:04:05.340 --> 02:04:06.340
it died.

1437
02:04:06.740 --> 02:04:08.759
And I know you're thinking. well. that's terrible

1438
02:04:08.783 --> 02:04:10.516
because that's a problem because we needed

1439
02:04:10.540 --> 02:04:13.105
to survive in the conditions of Venus. Obviously

1440
02:04:13.129 --> 02:04:15.536
I had to figure out how to breed a new strain

1441
02:04:15.560 --> 02:04:19.980
of nitrogen-resistant Taumoeba and guess what I used?

1442
02:04:20.600 --> 02:04:28.600
The breeder tanks that we made with your
Xenonite. And you know what? Now we're just

1443
02:04:29.120 --> 02:04:33.320
a couple of very cool dudes with their very
own strain of nitrogen resistant Taumoeba.

1444
02:04:34.620 --> 02:04:37.569
Really all we have to do now is breed enough

1445
02:04:37.593 --> 02:04:40.476
to survive the trip. And you got to wake up

1446
02:04:40.500 --> 02:04:47.276
because I don't know how to get
your half of the Taumoeba to Erid. So

1447
02:04:47.300 --> 02:04:51.780
no pressure. but we did make a deal.

1448
02:06:11.980 --> 02:06:13.380
Shhh.

1449
02:06:13.960 --> 02:06:14.960
Grace?

1450
02:06:20.170 --> 02:06:22.090
Rock. could you just.

1451
02:06:22.570 --> 02:06:23.010
I don't know.

1452
02:06:23.510 --> 02:06:24.510
Give me a little

1453
02:06:24.970 --> 02:06:25.970
chance. please.

1454
02:06:26.290 --> 02:06:27.290
to sleep a little?

1455
02:06:42.030 --> 02:06:44.550
Did we find Predator?

1456
02:06:52.670 --> 02:06:56.630
No is yes.

1457
02:07:11.770 --> 02:07:14.050
Amaze. Amaze. Amaze.

1458
02:07:14.690 --> 02:07:16.670
Rocky. Breeder Tank design.

1459
02:07:17.750 --> 02:07:18.330
Good job. bro.

1460
02:07:18.450 --> 02:07:19.446
We can go home.

1461
02:07:19.470 --> 02:07:20.470
Statement.

1462
02:07:22.890 --> 02:07:23.930
We can go home.

1463
02:07:25.150 --> 02:07:26.150
Fist my bump.

1464
02:07:27.370 --> 02:07:28.370
No.

1465
02:07:29.330 --> 02:07:30.330
That's still not right.

1466
02:07:30.810 --> 02:07:31.610
I'll do it.

1467
02:07:31.810 --> 02:07:33.090
Good. good. good.

1468
02:07:33.790 --> 02:07:35.250
So what we do now?

1469
02:07:35.490 --> 02:07:36.490
Question.

1470
02:07:40.870 --> 02:07:41.870
We party.

1471
02:07:55.250 --> 02:07:56.250
Wow.

1472
02:07:57.030 --> 02:07:58.930
