Rocky get one.

1477
02:08:06.650 --> 02:08:07.650
There you go.

1478
02:08:07.690 --> 02:08:08.690
It's good.

1479
02:08:09.890 --> 02:08:11.170
Oh. yeah.

1480
02:08:12.370 --> 02:08:14.710
Not much. just a little something.

1481
02:08:15.650 --> 02:08:16.670
Very own laptop.

1482
02:08:16.910 --> 02:08:18.346
My portable earth thinking machine.

1483
02:08:18.370 --> 02:08:20.610
With all human knowledge.

1484
02:08:21.070 --> 02:08:21.606
Thank you. thank you. thank you.

1485
02:08:21.630 --> 02:08:23.070
