And that assumes that the nations of
the world work together to ration food

1504
02:11:16.210 --> 02:11:24.210
which they won't. So I double the estimate.
And if you would truly care about

1505
02:11:24.670 --> 02:11:27.470
the children or anyone else for
that matter. you'd get on that ship.

1506
02:11:32.090 --> 02:11:40.090
I understand the stakes. I do. But I don't have it in me.

1507
02:11:49.350 --> 02:11:57.350
My mind is made up. I'm sorry.
but you just can't talk me into it.

1508
02:12:04.610 --> 02:12:12.610
I'm not trying to talk you into anything.
I am trying to make you understand

1509
02:12:16.310 --> 02:12:19.270
what I'm about to do next. Yeah. please.

1510
02:12:20.170 --> 02:12:22.310
Stay calm. Come in.

1511
02:12:25.490 --> 02:12:26.710
What is this?

1512
02:12:27.270 --> 02:12:30.630
Mission plan will state that we induced
your coma early to maximize your safety.

1513
02:12:31.110 --> 02:12:32.530
You will be remembered as a hero.

1514
02:12:33.590 --> 02:12:35.246
Come on. This is crazy.

1515
02:12:35.270 --> 02:12:36.450
I have to do it.

1516
02:12:36.490 --> 02:12:37.830
You're not. Come on.

1517
02:12:38.090 --> 02:12:39.110
What are you doing?

1518
02:12:39.850 --> 02:12:44.250
This may seem like me betraying you.
but it's actually me believing in you.

1519
02:12:44.350 --> 02:12:45.970
It sure feels like you're betraying me.

1520
02:12:46.670 --> 02:12:47.726
Don't make this harder. please.

1521
02:12:47.750 --> 02:12:48.750
Come on. I'm coming.

1522
02:12:52.050 --> 02:12:54.170
Let's keep talking about it.

1523
02:12:56.630 --> 02:12:58.630
Sit down and we do it differently.

1524
02:12:59.970 --> 02:13:00.970
Get out of here.

1525
02:13:06.830 --> 02:13:08.050
Yeah. he's running.

1526
02:13:25.350 --> 02:13:33.350
No! No! I can't do it! Don't
do it! Don't do it! Don't do it!

1527
02:13:36.770 --> 02:13:38.290
You know who you are.

1528
02:13:40.470 --> 02:13:41.630
You're going to do great.

1529
02:14:14.730 --> 02:14:16.890
I'm trying to think if there's anything I forgot.

1530
02:14:20.170 --> 02:14:22.170
Fuel tank fix. okay? Question?

1531
02:14:22.410 --> 02:14:23.846
Oh. yeah. yeah. They're working great.

1532
02:14:23.870 --> 02:14:25.850
Oh. good. Happy. happy. happy.

1533
02:14:33.010 --> 02:14:34.650
Well. my friend.

1534
02:14:35.710 --> 02:14:37.030
Yes. friend?

1535
02:14:38.510 --> 02:14:42.170
Not sure what to say. so I'm just going to...

1536
02:14:50.310 --> 02:14:51.310
Grace?

1537
02:14:55.390 --> 02:14:56.710
No one to watch you sleep.

1538
02:14:58.370 --> 02:14:59.370
Yeah.

1539
02:15:01.330 --> 02:15:03.750
You are very brave.

1540
02:15:06.250 --> 02:15:08.170
I don't know about that.

1541
02:15:11.170 --> 02:15:14.710
You are the bravest human I have ever met.

1542
02:15:16.390 --> 02:15:17.390
Hey.

1543
02:15:17.850 --> 02:15:18.526
It's a joke.

1544
02:15:18.550 --> 02:15:19.550
I know.

1545
02:15:20.170 --> 02:15:22.930
I only meet one human. and it's you.

1546
02:15:23.010 --> 02:15:24.010
I get it.

1547
02:15:24.690 --> 02:15:25.690
It's a good joke.

1548
02:15:25.890 --> 02:15:26.890
Good joke.

1549
02:15:27.930 --> 02:15:28.930
All right.

1550
02:15:34.350 --> 02:15:35.590
Well... Goodbye.

1551
