1571
02:20:27.730 --> 02:20:29.630
His life support systems will fail.

1572
02:20:32.330 --> 02:20:35.090
If that doesn't kill him the radiation sickness will.

1573
02:20:38.390 --> 02:20:41.770
He's looking at a long. slow.

1574
02:20:43.610 --> 02:20:45.490
painful death.

1575
02:20:48.450 --> 02:20:49.450
Alone.

1576
02:21:12.710 --> 02:21:14.030
I can't do both.

1577
02:21:16.190 --> 02:21:17.190
I can go home.

1578
02:21:20.850 --> 02:21:22.170
Or I can save.

1579
02:21:41.770 --> 02:21:44.690
I've sent you detailed logs of all of our findings

1580
02:21:45.390 --> 02:21:48.246
and enough Taumoeba for you to start

1581
02:21:48.270 --> 02:21:49.830
